it-sam-altman-xai-google-deepmind&quot;}]}&#39;>;&lt; /div>;&lt;/aside>;&lt;/div>; &lt;p id=&quot;vRSvmX&quot;>;至于反垄断指控，马斯克的律师声称 OpenAI 和微软“告诉...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/11/30/24309697/elon-musk-openai-lawsuit-for-profit-transition-preliminary-injunction&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/一个>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/11/30/24309697/elon-musk-openai-lawsuit-for-profit-transition-preliminary-injunction" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/11/30/24309697/elon-musk-openai-lawsuit-for-profit-transition-preliminary-injunction</id><author><name>韦斯·戴维斯</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-11-30T17:04:15-05:00</published><updated> 2024-11-30T17:04:15-05:00</updated><title>今天您仍然可以获得最好的黑色星期五优惠</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;黑色星期五在巨型秒表上销售产品。&quot; src =“https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/0OsslCAqBweoS5RtLC26h2D1pl0=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox -cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73756741/247350_CMBF_2024_EWinataBFDealsYouCanStillGet.0.png&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;图片：Elen Winata for The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p>;仅仅因为今天是星期六，并不意味着笔记本电脑、耳机和其他 Verge 认可的小工具的促销活动正在减少。 &lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24309106/best-black-friday-deals-2024-tech-gadgets-cyber-monday&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/24309106/best-black-friday-deals-2024-tech-gadgets-cyber-monday" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/24309106/best-black-friday-deals-2024-tech-gadgets-cyber-monday</id><author><name>安东尼奥·G·迪·贝内代托</name><name>希娜·瓦萨尼</name><name>昆汀·肯内默</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-11-30T16:00:00-05:00</published><updated> 2024-11-30T16:00:00-05:00</updated><title>这款高性能便携式移动电源目前仅售 74 美元</title><content type="html">&lt;图>; &lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/vwYAhZNElCmYzdwd8tsCl-tsCh0=/0x43:1024x726/131